27:11.888 --> 27:13.430
bouncing effect. So there's been an opportunity 
for our students to get to work for the banking

27:13.510 --> 27:21.280
community, the financial institutions, as well 
as the real estate and land development

27:21.766 --> 27:24.348
community. So that the planning accreditation 
guidelines of having this public sector base

27:25.750 --> 27:39.083
begins to get broadened through the way that we've 
been teaching in our classes.

27:42.246 --> 27:50.794
There's no doubt about it, your location is very 
advantageous for an urban planner. certainly

27:51.095 --> 27:54.559
much better than Austin or College Station. Next 
year you are facing the visiting team from the

27:56.262 --> 28:03.731
Accreditation Committee of APA.

